The paper deals with mechanism design, which is a subfield of game theory (cs.GT). It also uses optimal transport theory and duality theory, which are topics in information theory (cs.IT) and optimization (cs.DS), respectively. The paper also involves mathematical analysis and modeling (cs.MA) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques.
